Install 
---------

yum install couchdb

TO START
--------
terminal1 $ su -c 'couchdb'
Password:

terminal2 $ curl http://127.0.0.1:5984

RUN TEST SUITE
---------------
terminal3 $ firfox http://127.0.0.1:5984/_utils             <-- admin web interface, aka FUTON
Go in the Test suite tab
Click on [Run All]                                          <-- will run the test once by one!

PYTHON INSTERFACE
-----------------
easy_install couchdb
easy_install simplejson
easy_install couchapp
